import React from 'react'
import { NavItem } from '../nav-items/nav'
import { Icon } from '../icon'
import { Icom } from '../icom'

export const Header = () => {
  return (
    <header className='flex relative z-10 bg-blue  mt-3 pl- text-white rounded-[50px]'>
        <Icon /> 
        <nav className='flex space-x-6 ml-40 items-center'>
            <NavItem text='Предложения'/>
            <NavItem text='Калькулятор'/>
            <NavItem text='Статьи'/>
            <Icom text='Консультация'/>
        </nav> 
    </header>
    
  )
}
